/> </a></div></div></div><div class="main-wrap content-main-wrap"><div class="content-wrap"><main id="content" class="content-container"><div class="container layout-2-col layout-2-col-1 layout-right-sidebar post-template-9"><div class="row main-section"><div class="col-sm-8 content-column"><div class="single-container"><article id="post-9911" class="post-9911 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail  category-blog tag-bitmain tag-crypto tag-mining single-post-content"><div class="post-header-inner"><div class="post-header-title"><div class="term-badges floated"><span class="term-badge term-150"><a href="https://xbt.net/blog/">Blog</a></span></div><h1 class="single-post-title"> <span class="post-title" itemprop="headline">Mining Giant Bitmain Closes Down Amsterdam Facility Days After Exiting Texas</span></h1><div class="post-meta single-post-meta"> <a href="https://xbt.net/author/xbt-network/" title="Browse Author Articles" class="post-author-a post-author-avatar"> <img alt='' data-src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/89bd13a1ab0f9621d2ac831359ccda89?s=26&d=mm&r=g' class='avatar avatar-26 photo avatar-default' height='26' width='26' /><span class="post-author-name">By <b>XBT Network</b></span> </a> <span class="time"><time class="post-published updated" datetime="2019-01-18T09:40:55+00:00">Last updated <b>Jan 18, 2019</b></time></span></div></div></div><div class="post-share single-post-share top-share clearfix style-5"><div class="post-share-btn-group"> <a href="https://xbt.net/blog/mining-giant-bitmain-closes-down-amsterdam-facility-days-after-exiting-texas/#respond" class="post-share-btn post-share-btn-comments comments" title="Leave a comment on: &ldquo;Mining Giant Bitmain Closes Down Amsterdam Facility Days After Exiting Texas&rdquo;"><i class="bf-icon fa fa-comments" aria-hidden="true"></i> <b class="number">0</b></a></div><div class="share-handler-wrap "> <span class="share-handler post-share-btn rank-default"> <i class="bf-icon  f